quran[55]{c,v,t}:
  82,1,“Pamene thambo lidzasweke
  82,2,“Ndi pamene nyenyezi zidzayoyoke (ndi kumwazikana)
  82,3,“Pamenenso nyanja zikuluzikulu zidzaphwasulidwe
  82,4,“Ndiponso pamene manda adzafukulidwe (ndikutuluka akufa omwe adali mmenemo)
  82,5,“(Panthawiyo) mzimu uliwonse udzadziwa zimene udatsogoza (zabwino ndi zoipa) ndi zimene udasiya m’mbuyo
  82,6,“E iwe munthu! Nchiani chakunyenga kumsiya Mbuye wako wa ufulu (kufikira pomnyoza)
  82,7,“Amene adalenga iwe nakulinganiza (ziwalo zako) ndi kukulongosola (moyenera)
  82,8,“Ndipo maonekedwe amtundu uliwonse omwe adawafuna adakuveka (popanda chifuniro chako)
  82,9,"“Ayi, sichoncho! Koma inu mukutsutsa za (tsiku) lamalipiro"
  82,10,“Ndithu pa inu alipo okuyang’ anirani
  82,11,"“Olemekezeka, olemba (zochita zanu)"
  82,12,“Akudziwa (zonse) zimene mukuchita (zabwino ndi zoipa)
  82,13,“Ndithudi ochita zabwino adzakhala mu mtendere
  82,14,“Ndipo ndithu amene ali olakwira malamulo a Allah adzakhala ku Moto wopsereza
  82,15,“Adzaulowa tsiku la malipiro
  82,16,“Ndipo iwo kumeneko sadzachokako
  82,17,“Kodi nchiyani chingakudziwitse za tsiku la malipiro
  82,18,“Ndipo nchiyani chingakudziwitse za tsiku lamalipiro
  82,19,“Limeneli ndi tsiku limene mzimu uliwonse sudzakhala ndi mphamvu (yodzetsa mtendere kapena yochotsa chovuta) pa mzimu wina. Ndipo lamulo pa tsiku limeneli ndi la Allah yekha
  83,1,“Kuonongeka koopsa kukawapeza opunguza miyeso ya malonda
  83,2,“Amene amati akamadziyezera zinthu kwa anthu amafuna kulandira miyeso yodzadza
  83,3,“Koma pamene iwo akamawayesera pa muyeso wa mbale kapena wa sikelo amapungula (choyenera kulandira ogulawo)
  83,4,“Kodi amenewa (akupungula miyeso pamalondawo) sakuganiza kuti adzaukitsidwa
  83,5,“Pa tsiku lalikulu (ndiponso loopsa)
  83,6,“Tsiku limene adzaimilira anthu pamaso pa Mbuye wa zolengedwa
  83,7,“Ayi! Ndithu (siyani chinyengo pamalonda ndi kusalabadira kuuka mmanda); zolembedwa za ntchito ya oipa zili mu Sijjin
  83,8,“Nanga nchiyani chitakudziwitse za Sijjin
  83,9,“Ameneyu ndi kaundula wamkulu yemwe walembedwa (mkati mwake ntchito za anthu oipa)
  83,10,“Chilango chaukali tsiku limenelo chili pa otsutsa
  83,11,“Amene akutsutsa za tsiku la malipiro
  83,12,"“Ndipo palibe angalitsutse koma yekhayo wopyola malire (pochita zoipa), wa machimo ambiri"
  83,13,"“Pamene ma Ayah Athu akuwerengedwa kwa iye (onena za tsiku la malipiro ndikuuka mmanda) amanena kuti: “Izi ndi nthano za anthu akale.”"
  83,14,"“Iyayi, sichoncho! Koma yaphimbidwa mitima yawo ndi dzimbiri (la machimo) omwe akhala akukolola"
  83,15,“Ayi ndithu iwo (okanira) tsiku limenelo) adzatchingidwa kwa Mbuye wawo; (sadzamuona)
  83,16,“Pambuyo pake adzalowa ku Moto; (oyaka)
  83,17,“Kenaka adzauzidwa (powaliritsa) “Ichi nchilango chomwe mudali kuchitsutsa (pa dziko lapansi).”
  83,18,"“Zoona, ndithu kaundula wa anthu abwino (ochita ntchito zabwino) ali mu Illiyyun"
  83,19,“Nanga nchiyani chitakudziwitse za Illiyyun
  83,20,“Ameneyu ndi kaundula (wamkulu) yemwe walembedwa (mkati mwake ntchito za anthu abwino)
  83,21,“Amamuyikira umboni (angelo) amene ayandikitsidwa (kwa Allah)
  83,22,“Ndithu ochita zabwino adzakhala mu mtendere
  83,23,“Atakhala pa mipando ya ulemu uku akuyang’ana (zimene Allah wawapatsa monga mtendere ndi ulemelero)
  83,24,“Udzaona kuwala kwa mtendere pa nkhope zawo
  83,25,“Adzamwetsedwa vinyo (woyeretsedwa) wotsekeredwa ndi zitsekerero zolimba
  83,26,"“Komalizira kwake (kwa vinyoyo) kuzikatuluka fungo la misk; kuti akapeze zimenezi, apikisane opikisana"
  83,27,“Ndipo chosakanizira cha vinyoyo ndi madzi a Tasnim
  83,28,“(Tasnim ameneyo) ndi kasupe amene azikamwa amene ayandikitsidwa (kwa Allah)
  83,29,“Ndithu amene adachita machimo adali kuwaseka (mwachipongwe) okhulupirira (pa dziko lapansi)
  83,30,“(Okhulupirira) akadutsa pafupi ndi iwo ankakodolerana maso (mwachipongwe)
  83,31,“Ndipo akabwerera kwa anzawo amabwerera akusangalala (ndi kunyozedwa kwa okhulupirira)
  83,32,"“Ndipo (nthawi zonse) akawaona Asilamu amanena: “Ndithu awa ndi osokera (chifukwa chomkhulupirira Mtumiki).” (s.a.w)"
  83,33,“Sanatumizidwe (Akafiri) kukhala ayang’aniri kwa okhulupirira (ndikuwaweruza zakulungama ndi kusokera)
  83,34,“Basi lero okhulupirira awaseka osakhulupirira (powabwezera chipongwe chawo chimene ankachita pa dziko lapansi)
  83,35,“Atakhala pa mipando ya ulemu uku akuyang’ana (mtendere umene Allah wawapatsa)
  83,36,“Kodi alipidwa osakhulupirira pa zomwe ankachita zija (pa dziko lapansi)